# Rust / WASM rules

- Keep wasm-bindgen exports minimal: `get_image_info`, `process_image`
- Pass options as JSON string, not per-field bindgen
- All user errors return `{ code, message }` via JsValue
- Avoid panics on bad input — return `PicooError`
- `wasm-pack` profile: `wasm-opt = false` (run wasm-opt in build.sh with SIMD flags)
- After changes: `cargo test` and `cargo clippy -- -D warnings`

## WebP on WASM

Use `zenwebp`: lossy VP8 by default (`quality` 1–100), `lossless: true` for VP8L. `maxSizeKB` runs quality binary search for lossy WebP; lossless WebP only shrinks dimensions when `autoResize` is enabled.
